{"tid":781559,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度時報：洞朗對峙週年 中共軍爆扮游牧民族入侵拉達克","createTime":"2018-08-16T03:38:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T04:27:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5cec6fd2e8b0cf56855d8c8609ce44907fb1532f","tid":781559,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/71TSsC33jidQ9wdp674.Ag--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/newtalk.tw/2236d7fee23b5aab5f0ac9c6da4b1814\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F71TSsC33jidQ9wdp674.Ag--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnewtalk.tw%2F2236d7fee23b5aab5f0ac9c6da4b1814&h=c9aa132b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼去年雙方在洞朗地區對峙數月後，《印度時報》（Times of India）報導，解放軍再度入侵，這回竟然穿著游牧民族服裝，從7月第1周起，從拉達克東部巴里加斯（Demchok）的實際控制線「入侵」300~400公尺，並在當地駐紮5個帳棚兵力，後經印度多次舉布條要求撤離，才撤去3棚，仍留有2棚士兵。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，拉達克（Ladakh）是該地地區23個有爭議的地區之一，從拉達克東部一直延伸到阿魯納恰爾邦，還有Chumar，Pangong Tso和Dumchele等地，由於中、印「不同的看法」，雙方經常在邊界發生衝突。印方報告指出，今年至今為止，中國已有170次入侵，2016年為273次，2017年為426次；而去年在洞朗（Doklam）兩軍之間長達73天的對峙，更引爆2國之間的外交爭端。<br />\n<br />\n儘管去年6月，印度暫時把中國拒於門外，也將道路建設擴展到洞朗南部Jampheri山脈，但中國解放軍早就在北洞朗建造軍事基礎設施，包括直升機停機坪，並留有600~700人的部隊駐守。<br />\n<br />\n此次解放軍再傳「入侵」拉達克，有消息指出，可能是因為不滿拉達克政府試圖在能龍（Nerlong）修築小路。據了解，拉達克是藏族傳統居住地區，現由印度控制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B4%9E%E6%9C%97%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99%E9%80%B1%E5%B9%B4-%E4%B8%AD%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E7%88%86%E6%89%AE%E6%B8%B8%E7%89%A7%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%B2%E6%8B%89%E9%81%94%E5%85%8B-020135839.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B4%259E%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%25B0%258D%25E5%25B3%2599%25E9%2580%25B1%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BB%258D%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2589%25AE%25E6%25B8%25B8%25E7%2589%25A7%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%258E%25A8%25E9%2580%25B2%25E6%258B%2589%25E9%2581%2594%25E5%2585%258B-020135839.html&d=mvgydw%2BwIV3EwqjE35xrrDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=6fd3232c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B4%9E%E6%9C%97%E5%B0%8D%E5%B3%99%E9%80%B1%E5%B9%B4-%E4%B8%AD%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BE%E8%BB%8D%E7%88%86%E6%89%AE%E6%B8%B8%E7%89%A7%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%B2%E6%8B%89%E9%81%94%E5%85%8B-020135839.html</a>"},{"pid":"8a28e6800af129bf56f344fc8fc668615be6695f","tid":781559,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:39:59.000Z","msg":"都係虛張聲勢多，要打一早打咗。"},{"pid":"8c7870147bcec5ee74229749035cb2d70a8a6674","tid":781559,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T03:48:20.000Z","msg":"..... &quot;進入&quot; 香港就扮香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7f2f146070e12c970897924d45511d7ce95886","tid":781559,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"印度加油"},{"pid":"00ac545611a2b2bb05f1295f30ccbb319a3bf0c5","tid":781559,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c7f2f146070e12c970897924d45511d7ce95886","tid":781559,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T04:51:27.000Z","msg":"印度加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T10:24:21.000Z","msg":"睇錯 <br />\n印度神油"},{"pid":"e990e7d66d1f23cae53b64deb30195f9e7a77e14","tid":781559,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}